    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "idk im not so sure about that. i've been looking at the specs for the new model and it seems way more \"robotic.\" i'm worried our regulars will hate it because it lacks the nuance you have. maybe we should be more honest and let them know that while it's faster, it might struggle with the really complicated, custom itineraries that you usually handle so easily? just being real with them so they don't complain later.",
